summary: 6:00 am PART 3 1 year later...[[MORE]] ___ sallybee @dangerousarianas 1203 following 12k followers ___ He's a male. 21 years...
body:
6:00 am

PART 3

1 year later…

___

sallybee

@dangerousarianas

1203 following

12k followers

___

He’s a male. 21 years old. Works in Chicago in some Club so sleeps in the morning and works at night. Loves Charlie Puth and photography. His mom’s korean and his dad’s American, so he often goes to Korea. I have never seen him. No photo. No face. Nothing. Just that stupid bird on the icon.

I know. I’m a fucking asshole. I know he’s lying and I bet his a 47 male man waiting for me to send nudes but, who cares? I never loved talking to someone that much and so, I’ll stay just for a bit more, even thought he may kidnap me.

___

I’ve been hacked twice in my whole life. These 2 times gave me a trauma.

The first one was all my fault. Liking through messages transformed my facebook into a French persona. The following one wasn’t an actual hack. I shared a photo of mine in a chatroom, (look at the dumb me) and this guy used it against me. The photo was nothing amazing so he left me alone but I fear the day he comes back and throws shade on me.

I get nervous really quickly and so, I try not to expose myself fully, but this time I couldn’t. He was everything I never had and so, once in the blue moon, I decided to risk my sanity to a stranger.

And to your question I do. I promise I do. Do you? I can’t tell when you are telling the truth or lying. Am I just one of your internet friends? Do you still feel lonely? Are you who you tell to be? Can you even answer this question? Are you even there?
